00:18:18,820 --> 00:18:19,940
 What is the next thing?

275
00:18:19,940 --> 00:18:21,160
 What is the next promotion?

276
00:18:21,160 --> 00:18:22,540
 What is the next relationship?

277
00:18:22,540 --> 00:18:26,020
 What are the next followers that I can get if I post at this particular time and do this

