00:18:26,020 --> 00:18:27,940
 particular thing with my reel?

279
00:18:27,940 --> 00:18:28,940
 What what what?

280
00:18:28,940 --> 00:18:32,140
 Our focus so often as high achievers is what can I gain?

281
00:18:32,140 --> 00:18:33,140
 What can I grow in?

282
00:18:33,140 --> 00:18:34,320
 What can I do?

283
00:18:34,320 --> 00:18:35,980
 What can I grow up with?

284
00:18:35,980 --> 00:18:41,100
 And Jesus shows up and says, "You're asking what so much that you've forgotten the most

