00:18:50,220 --> 00:18:56,020
 It's almost as if the behavior, which can be destructive, is not actually the main issue

288
00:18:56,020 --> 00:19:01,980
 because the behavior is being driven by a motive.

289
00:19:01,980 --> 00:19:07,740
 Jesus is saying, "You need to wrestle, Saul, with this motive."

