00:19:21,220 --> 00:19:27,100
 And the starting point of that whole process is Saul recognizing that there are probably

294
00:19:27,100 --> 00:19:28,580
 some things within him.

295
00:19:28,580 --> 00:19:33,260
 There are probably some things that are unmet needs, unmet healing, all the stuff that's

296
00:19:33,260 --> 00:19:36,380
 gone in his upbringing, all the stuff where he's trying to prove himself.

297
00:19:36,380 --> 00:19:41,840
 There's a whole lot of dark and bad stuff within him that he doesn't want to deal with.

298
00:19:41,840 --> 00:19:48,900
 And actually his selfish ambition is designed to cover all that up.

299
00:19:48,900 --> 00:19:53,460
 So many of us very high achievers, we are pushing ourselves and we're going and going

